### Create category
POST {{host}}/catalog/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Camisetas",
  "ncmCode": "6109.10.00"
}

###

### List categories
GET {{host}}/catalog/categories?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Search categories by prefix (typeahead)
GET {{host}}/catalog/categories?q=Cam&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get category by ID
GET {{host}}/catalog/categories/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Rename category
PUT {{host}}/catalog/categories/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Camisetas Manga Curta",
  "ncmCode": "6109.10.00"
}

###

### Delete category
DELETE {{host}}/catalog/categories/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
